135
00:18:20,408 --> 00:18:24,064
Zato što volim da fotografišem noću.

136
00:18:24,238 --> 00:18:26,327
Šta radite, gospođo?

137
00:19:22,166 --> 00:19:23,602
Nisam voleo mog oca.

138
00:19:26,213 --> 00:19:28,572
On mi je jasno dao do znanja
da ni on ne voli mene.

139
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:35,135
Posle smrti moje majke...

140
00:19:38,747 --> 00:19:40,401
On me je zaključao u podrum.

141
00:19:42,142 --> 00:19:43,274
