Licem napred.

189
00:24:39,570 --> 00:24:40,773
Da li ga vidite?

190
00:24:50,450 --> 00:24:51,799
Broj dva.

191
00:24:54,498 --> 00:24:55,847
Broj dva, iskorači napred.

192
00:24:59,851 --> 00:25:01,026
Da li je to on?

193
00:25:05,334 --> 00:25:08,512
