523
01:12:51,418 --> 01:12:52,724
tvog muža.

524
01:13:01,338 --> 01:13:02,948
Oh, moj--

525
01:13:03,122 --> 01:13:04,515
Oh, moj bože.

526
01:13:07,430 --> 01:13:08,780
